reviewText: The dvd is OK...But if you google him you will find a couple of free articles that contain 95% of what he shared here. I was disappointed that he didn't go into more detail about his lures (all his lures) and his boat. I know he mostly fishes for his trophy bass at night, but wish he had demonstrated his techniques and presentations with a daytime on the water demo.
Very informative and interesting. Best video on how to catch a big bass.
I bought this for my husband and it was not as great as he expected it to be.
Shipped in very timely manner, we'll pleased with order, now headed to the lake to try what I learned from dvd.
Great video on how to find big fish when fishing at night! This is a must have DVD! Worth every penny!
